00:16:21,326 --> 00:16:24,047
In order for competitive communities to thrive,

394
00:16:24,047 --> 00:16:25,068
they need competitive events.

395
00:16:25,068 --> 00:16:27,429
A healthy community has frequent events

396
00:16:27,429 --> 00:16:28,850
and you're gonna need to pay for all of that

397
00:16:28,850 --> 00:16:31,211
and sometimes tournament entrance fees alone

398
00:16:31,211 --> 00:16:32,032
may not be enough.

399
00:16:32,032 --> 00:16:35,254
Bumble Bear encourages people to host their own tournaments

400
00:16:35,254 --> 00:16:37,495
and to find their own sponsorships for these events.

401
00:16:37,495 --> 00:16:39,996
In general, Bumble Bear's opening to letting folks

402
00:16:39,996 --> 00:16:41,858
arrange their own events as long as it doesn't appear

403
00:16:41,858 --> 00:16:44,879
to look like it is an event endorsed or sponsored directly

404
00:16:44,879 --> 00:16:46,580
by Bumble Bear or Killer Queen Arcade.

405
00:16:47,632 --> 00:16:49,293
Killer Queen Arcade has also gotten to the point now

406
00:16:49,293 --> 00:16:50,734
we have been lucky enough to have the attention

407
00:16:50,734 --> 00:16:52,115
of some of the largest sponsors

408
00:16:52,115 --> 00:16:53,676
and marketing brands like Red Bull.

409
00:16:53,676 --> 00:16:55,137
It is through a lot of hard work from people

410
00:16:55,137 --> 00:16:56,959
within our community and within Bumble Bear

411
00:16:56,959 --> 00:16:58,980
that has raised KQ's profile to this level.

412
00:17:00,665 --> 00:17:05,190
Because the game's located in a lot of bars, beer sponsors are a great sponsorship source for us.

413
00:17:05,190 --> 00:17:09,194
These are two events, one in Portland and one in Minneapolis,

