00:18:11,655 --> 00:18:12,836
In addition to beer companies,

442
00:18:12,836 --> 00:18:15,298
there's a wide variety of gaming adjacent companies

443
00:18:15,298 --> 00:18:16,819
that are willing to sponsor game events.

444
00:18:16,819 --> 00:18:19,821
Food and beverage, which can include anything

445
00:18:19,821 --> 00:18:21,803
from snack distributors to local restaurants.

