00:24:06,970 --> 00:24:09,691
I can't stress the importance of working with your community

586
00:24:09,691 --> 00:24:11,771
and enabling them to do cool stuff with your game

587
00:24:11,771 --> 00:24:13,072
when you're an indie.

588
00:24:13,072 --> 00:24:15,112
They can surprise you with what they're capable of doing,

589
00:24:15,112 --> 00:24:18,373
and they are literally the lifeblood of your game.

